Mathieu-J-P.  Stack-B-H.  Dick-W-C.  Buchanan-W-W.

Pulmonary infection and rheumatoid arthritis.

ARTHRITIS-RHEUMATOID: co.  BRONCHIECTASIS: co.  CYSTIC-FIBROSIS: co.

ADOLESCENCE.  ADULT.  ARTHRITIS-RHEUMATOID: im.  FEMALE.  HUMAN.
MALE.  RESPIRATORY-FUNCTION-TESTS.  RHEUMATOID-FACTOR: an.

Five of eleven patients with bronchiectasis and/or cystic fibrosis
developed a polyarthritis with positive tests for rheumatoid factor.
Possible mechanisms of this complication are discussed.

